Body: Description: Hello, I have updated PingCastle to the latest version, but after running it, I received an error. I have downloaded and installed the latest version of ASP.NET, but I still could not open the page and access the settings to configure it.

What We've Learned Updated: Customer getting errors after upgrading ASP.NET. As I can see in the screenshot, he installed v9. 
PingCastle supports v8.xx
Next Steps Updated: Wait for customer to install ASP.NET 8.xx
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
